verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Brothers, sisters, we are one,
And our life has just begun;
In the Spirit we are young;
We can live forever.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Shout together to the Lord,
Who has promised our reward;
Happiness a hundredfold;
And we’ll live forever.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Jesus gave a new command,
That we love our fellow men;
‘Til we’ve reached the Promised Land.
Where we’ll live forever.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}If we want to live with Him,
We must also die with Him;
Die to selfishness and sin,
And we’ll rise forever.{/lang-eng}
